自己的自由嗎？（責任編輯：黃梅茹）<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://buzzorange.com/2019/03/13/girl-call-herself-taiwanese-to-pro-china/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbuzzorange.com%2F2019%2F03%2F13%2Fgirl-call-herself-taiwanese-to-pro-china%2F&d=U4JEvS4lHdpitRbH3ga0O1hCriQ9KcwZROA2Rh0I8Zw%3D&h=8bec82db\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://buzzorange.com/2019/03/13/girl-call-herself-taiwanese-to-pro-china/</a>"},{"pid":"5e83ae8078dd7842053bd75727f9aeafbefab723","tid":1283939,"uid":149978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"74421974b8a6d37b0e60e0553a7ba8aa33090a99","tid":1283939,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ffc65ec5d57191dbd150aa5ae60a84a3750a8acd","tid":1283939,"uid":109701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T03:34:13.000Z","msg":"先3年咋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T03:46:15.000Z","msg":"500萬以下罰金<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n如果係新移民應該取消戶籍"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-17T01:58:38.000Z","msg":"對"}]}